from langflow import CustomComponent
from langchain.embeddings.fake import FakeEmbeddings
from langflow.field_typing import Embeddings


class Component(CustomComponent):
    display_name: str = "Fake Embeddings"
    description: str = "Generates fake vector embeddings from documents. Used for experimentation purposes."

    def build(self, size:int=300) -> Embeddings:
        embeddings = FakeEmbeddings(size=size)
        self.status = embeddings
        return embeddings
